TLS support can be enabled in the chart by specifying the *tls.* parameters at deployment time. The following parameters can be used:

* Encrypt client communication using TLS certificates:

~~~
auth.client.secureTransport: true
~~~

* Enable host authentication using TLS certificates:

~~~
auth.client.enableAuthentication: true
~~~

* Encrypt peer communication using TLS certificates:

~~~
auth.peer.secureTransport: true
~~~

* Automatically create the TLS certificates:

~~~
auth.peer.useAutoTLS: true
~~~
